    { "id": "legend", "type": "rectangle", "x": 1420, "y": 15, "width": 360, "height": 380,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 96, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 96,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "legend-text"}], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false },
    { "id": "legend-text", "type": "text", "x": 1430, "y": 25, "width": 340, "height": 360,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 97, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 97,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "LEGEND\n\nModule — Robot subsystem with\n  typed In[T]/Out[T] streams\n\nBlueprint — autoconnect() recipe\n  wiring modules together\n\n@skill — LLM-callable function\n  exposed via RPC\n\nLCM — Low-latency Communications\n  inter-module message bus\n\nMCP — Model Context Protocol\n  TCP:9990, exposes skills\n  to external AI clients\n\nRxPy Observable — reactive event\n  stream with BackPressure\n\nReAct — Reason + Act agent loop\n  (LangGraph state machine)",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "legend", "originalText": "LEGEND\n\nModule — Robot subsystem with\n  typed In[T]/Out[T] streams\n\nBlueprint — autoconnect() recipe\n  wiring modules together\n\n@skill — LLM-callable function\n  exposed via RPC\n\nLCM — Low-latency Communications\n  inter-module message bus\n\nMCP — Model Context Protocol\n  TCP:9990, exposes skills\n  to external AI clients\n\nRxPy Observable — reactive event\n  stream with BackPressure\n\nReAct — Reason + Act agent loop\n  (LangGraph state machine)", "lineHeight": 1.25 },

